Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang mau kasus "Kroket"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kuserahkan padamu, Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kroket?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mike, apa itu kasus "Kroket"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hugh, kamu belum pernah\Nmenyelesaikan kasus "Kroket", ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu singkatan,\N"Kalau Rusak, Oke".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mike, kamu suka kasus kroket?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak perlu terlalu khawatir\Nseperti kasus lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah selesai\Ndengan penyiksaan hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku baru menyelesaikan yang terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengenalnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada pria yang tidak kami kenal di koridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mungkin Fon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu, boleh aku minta tanda tanganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu dekat dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mungkin akan menjualmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero, aku bisa mendengarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat, dia akan membungkamku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, aku ini cuma
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pemulung yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemulung?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sampah setelah kita selesai menyiksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tidak bisa membiarkan mereka\Nkembali ke publik, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tugasku adalah mengurus mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari wajah, tubuh, gelar,\Ndan koneksi mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak ada yang boleh disia-siakan\Ndari para penjahat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua bagian bisa dimakan, seperti salmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak suka\Nsaat kamu mengatakan hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa kalian yang bertanggung jawab\Natas pria "Kroket" itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kami membuat kesalahan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kondisinya masih baik setelah disiksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya kupikir kalian\Nmungkin baru di Spirytus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kasus "Kroket" diserahkan\Nke perusahaan lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka bisa meninggalkan kekacauan besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekacauan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Besar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekacauan besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hera, bagaimana bisnismu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lumayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noe, ini tagihan bulan lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, harganya naik ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, mulai sekarang,\Nkami akan menagihmu dengan tarif ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah menagih kami\Nlebih dari yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau barangnya dalam kondisi baik,\Nharga sebelumnya harus tetap sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salah satu distributor kami\Nbangkrut baru-baru ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak menaikkan harga,\Nkami tidak bisa bertahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hera, kamu makhluk terindah di Bumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya sepuluh persen, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, sudah lama aku tidak melihatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tampak berantakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tidak terlalu buruk\Nuntuk mengganggu wilayah orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang melakukan urusannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa masih ada perbedaan wilayah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kamu ingin memulai\Nperusahaan penyiksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendengaranmu masih bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap ini sebagai hadiah cepat sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan koneksi\Ndan informasi yang tertulis di sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu bisa memulai perusahaan dengan mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku boleh menerima ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, aku juga sudah menghapalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tiba-tiba muncul untuk memberikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada maksud tersembunyi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, aku hanya bersikap baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau punya motif tersembunyi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menurutku itu investasi awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong pekerjakan jasaku\Nsaat kamu memulai perusahaan baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Negosiasi harga selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh kumasukkan barangnya sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan biarkan senyum itu menipumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia punya banyak cara\Nuntuk menghadapi orang jahat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti orang jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesepakatan yang menguntungkan,\Ntapi kamu sangat tak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu, Siu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melindungimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan takut, dia sudah pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, kalian bisa kubawa nanti, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya Sero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah banyak pendatang baru berbakat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu terus membahas itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan siksaan berkualitas tinggi\Ndari Spirytus,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa menghasilkan lebih banyak uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tujuanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hanya salah satunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu muncul kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, ada mesin baru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reaksimu terlalu santai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu penyiksa dan penulis novel horor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu takutkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketakutan akan manusia hidup\Ndan hantu itu berbeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah seharusnya kamu lebih takut\Natau menyangkal keberadaan hantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mungkin takut\Nkalau mereka muncul di rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, ini perusahaan penyiksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah wajar jika ada hantu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau bekerja\Ndi tempat yang ada hantunya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lepaskan aku!\N- Kenapa hantu muncul di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kamu sungguh melihatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, ada bayangan aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ada suara seperti teriakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dipikirkan terus,\Npekerjaanmu bisa terganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan tinggalkan aku\Nsendirian di kantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita hanya perlu membuktikan\Ntidak ada apa-apa di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, mari kita menginap\Ndi kantor untuk semalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mau menginap?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil Hera mengizinkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi untuk berjaga-jaga,\Nbisakah kamu tetap di sini juga, Siu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak percaya hal itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ada serangan di beberapa\Nperusahaan penyiksaan belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang mencurigakan\Nmungkin menyelinap masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ketemu,\Nkami bisa membunuhnya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih mudah daripada menghadapi hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat bisa diandalkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maaf sudah merepotkanmu,\Npadahal kamu punya anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hera dan Noe akan menjaga mereka,\Njadi jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reu! Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berdua akan menginap malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tidak bertemu, Noe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, lama tidak bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga, Paman Hera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harus memanggilku "kakak".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini punyaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ini untuk Siu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia makan banyak seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia makan sangat sedikit seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya terbalik?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suhu airnya enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyenangkan ada pemandian umum\Nseperti ini di kantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jarang menggunakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu mendadak mulai menggunakannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu saat dia pulang kantor\Ndengan penuh darah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang melapor polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari istirahat\Nsampai kita menemukan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:10:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya ada tiga ranjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hugh, pakai ranjang tunggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lebih besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku bisa tidur di mana saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa, pakai saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tidur di ranjang atas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa terlalu sempit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu dengar itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita bunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tinggalkan aku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh, suaranya dari arah sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya di atas sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero, angkat aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat, dia tidak ragu sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelaku yang membuatmu sangat ketakutan\Nhanya keluarga kucing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira itu hantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, menyenangkan bisa bermalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kita bermalam bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kamu tertidur,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu dan aku menangkap hal lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada kucing lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyerang perusahaan penyiksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah memang ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada dua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Spirytus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perusahaan macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perusahaan penyiksaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kena kamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelaku tertangkap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya dia serangga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mengintai di depan kantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada rumor tentang penyerang\Nperusahaan penyiksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, dia masih pelajar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lepaskan saja dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengenalnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia adikku, Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kamu tak mau\Nmemberitahuku pekerjaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Kak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku sedang bekerja.\NTelepon aku nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu pekerjaanmu menyiksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu tidak memberitahuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu merahasiakan\Npekerjaan ini dariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar saja kamu merasa jijik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu biasanya pulang sesekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa akhir pekan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku harus bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku ada janji\Nbermain dengan putri kolega seniorku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sama sekali tidak peduli padaku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak yang kusukai tidak seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat terobsesi dengan kakaknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti menyenangkan punya adik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuatmu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pulang bersamamu hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan nakal dan tunggu aku nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero, adikmu pasti sulit dihadapi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat menyayangimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengerti, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia sedang dalam\Nfase memberontak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya, dia benci padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat kesepian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia tidak menyadarinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakakku jauh lebih tua dariku\Ndan aku bangga padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pandai dalam pelajaran dan olahraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu populer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga sangat menyayangiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi belakangan ini,\Ndia hanya terus bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaannya juga aneh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu keterlaluan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, adiknya Sero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu Siu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kenapa bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakakku tidak banyak bercerita\Ntentang pekerjaannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia membicarakan\Nhal yang terjadi di kantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia membicarakanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya kolega senior bernama Siu\Ndan dia sungguh luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat cepat\Ndan mahir dalam pekerjaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, dia sangat menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, dia bisa diandalkan dalam segala hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku menikmati pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jijik amat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cemburu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena kamu memonopoli kakakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal dia kakakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kamu bilang ini pekerjaan aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kamu tidak mau Sero menyiksa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pandai dalam segala hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa harus pekerjaan\Nyang tidak diinginkan kebanyakan orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ingat penculikan berantai\Nyang ada di berita bulan lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero yang mendapatkan\Ninformasi lokasi para korban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu semua korbannya selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pekerjaan\Nyang hanya bisa dilakukan olehnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kakakku melakukan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bisa melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa dia bersaing dengan kakakku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Kakak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena aku berpikir\Npekerjaanmu menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan belajar lebih banyak\Ntentang penyiksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luke, kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah dirimu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kabar adikmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mau bicara denganku sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa fase memberontaknya akan berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia masih berpikir itu fase memberontak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada kasus yang kamu pecahkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua kasus ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu ingin tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin tahu\Napa kamu bekerja keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menjadi anak aneh yang membuat\Nkliping berita tentang kejahatan besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mulai bersikap seperti penggemar aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu, apa pekerjaanmu baru selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya selesai lebih cepat dari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak fokus hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajahmu memerah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus segera pulang,\Ntapi ada satu kasus lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kamu harus pulang sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam, lepaskan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sakit,\Njadi lakukan saja sesuai perintah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak percaya dia berlagak tangguh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku akan tamat saat dia bangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reu dan Nero juga sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, apa aku membangunkan kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku mendengar suara,\Njadi aku datang untuk memeriksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Papa kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terlihat seperti seorang putri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Turunkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian demam tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu datang untuk bermain, Sero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan datang lagi\Nsaat kalian sudah sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Papa juga sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia tertular dari kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dia baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu baik-baik saja, jadi tidurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kami butuh bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah bangun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reu dan Nero sedang istirahat\Ndi kamar mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak mau mereka melihatmu lemah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ekspresimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ekspresi sok tahumu\Nbenar-benar membuatku kesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu pujian?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan pujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja, aku sudah minta bantuan\Nuntuk menjaga mereka berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena meminta mereka datang\Ntanpa izinmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga, Siu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah dan pulihkan kekuatanmu!\NBuka mulutmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu meremehkanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku terbiasa\Nmenjaga adikku seperti ini, jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mike dan Hugh,\Npekerjaan kalian sama dengan Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti apa Papa di kantor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia keren sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siu selalu membantu kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Papa sangat keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak sabar melakukan\Npekerjaan yang sama dengan Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian anak-anak yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menghabiskan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga menyiapkan makan malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tidak keberatan, makanlah nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf soal hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibandingkan yang selalu\Nkamu lakukan untukku,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setidaknya ini yang bisa kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak sia-sia aku melatihmu selama ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu tidak tetap seperti ini, Siu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mau berkelahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak perlu mengantar kami keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harus beristirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jauh lebih baik sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengurus diriku sendiri\Nagar tidak merepotkan kalian lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah di kantor atau rumah,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu bisa mengandalkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami pasti bisa membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Papa, apa ada kabar baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bicara dengan mulut penuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
